    public class MultilineTextField
extends TextfieldBase<com.google.gwt.user.client.ui.TextArea>
    A MultilineTextField is a TextfieldBase wrapped around a TextArea. It adds specific behaviors related to text areas such as the minimum displayed rows count and the maximum amount of lines that can be input by the user.
    Author:
    Mohamed Ilyes DIMASSI
